    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A group of triclinic feldspar distinguished from alkali feldspars which are sodium- or potassium-rich.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
